==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: zì gŭ hóngyán duō bómìng
===Etymology===
*From the ''[[w:Journey to the West|Journey to the West]]''
**Literally: From ancient times, many with a rosy countenance have been ill-fated.
===Proverb===
'''[[自]][[古]][[红颜]][[多]][[薄命]]'''
# From ancient times, beautiful women have often been ill-fated.
===Alternative forms===
[[自古紅顏多薄命]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])
